OL,7,FTwo teenage boys have been left
OL,8,F"broken" after a teacher pretending to
OL,9,Fbe a 16-year-old girl tricked them
OL,10,Finto sending him intimate images of
OL,11,Fthemselves.
OL,13,FDaniel Fuge, 38, of Prospect Road,
OL,14,FDorchester, Dorset, had been working
OL,15,Fas a primary school teacher in Saudi
OL,16,FArabia.
