OL,5,Cthemselves
OL,7,FHe has been sentenced at Mold Crown
OL,8,FCourt to seven years for inciting a
OL,9,Fboy to engage in sexual activity with
OL,10,Fpenetration, and jailed for a further
OL,11,Fthree years for the same offence
OL,12,Fwithout penetration against a second
OL,13,Fboy.
OL,15,FHis sentencing comes after he was
OL,16,Ffound guilty of the offences by a jury
OL,17,Flast month.
