OL,7,FEric Lamb, prosecuting, told the court
OL,8,Fthat Fuge posed as a 16-year-old girl
OL,9,Fand encouraged the first boy, 13, to
OL,10,Fsend naked photos of himself.
OL,12,FHe then incited the boy to send a
OL,13,Fvideo of himself carrying out a sexual
OL,14,Fact. Police investigated and found
OL,15,Fsomeone using the same account had
OL,16,Falso incited a second boy, 14, to send
OL,17,FFuge naked photos of himself.
