OL,7,FNicholas Williams, defending, said
OL,8,FFuge had incited the video of the
OL,9,Ffirst victim and shared the video with
OL,10,Fthe second victim.
OL,12,FBut "someone else" had then taken the
OL,13,Fsecond victim's phone, found the video
OL,14,Fand posted it around the school.
OL,16,FFuge's devices in Wrexham, where his
OL,17,Ffather lives, were found to contain
OL,18,Ffive indecent images of children in
OL,19,Fcategory C.
