OL,7,FAddressing Fuge, who was on a video
OL,8,Flink from HMP Berwyn, he added: "My
OL,9,Fwife and I feared our son would commit
OL,10,Fsuicide because of your lurid
OL,11,Fbearings."
OL,13,FHe continued: "It's your turn to feel
OL,14,Fashamed, it's your turn to feel
OL,15,Fembarrassed, it's your turn to feel
OL,16,Ffear of what might happen," he said.
OL,18,FThe mother of the second victim said
OL,19,Fin a statement, read by the
OL,20,Fprosecutor, that she was worried about
OL,21,Fher "broken boy."
