OL,7,FHer statement said that she was
OL,8,Ffrightened he could take his own life
OL,9,Fand checked on him every hour. She
OL,10,Fsaid she was "so pleased" that both
OL,11,Fboys "are still here with us".
OL,13,FShe added: "You may have stolen their
OL,14,Fchildhood but you won't steal their
OL,15,Ffuture."
OL,17,FMr Williams said it was "worrying"
OL,18,Fthat his client had been a primary
OL,19,Fschool teacher, but said that there
OL,20,Fwas no link between his crimes and any
OL,21,Fpupils in the Middle East.
