OL,7,FThe judge, His Honour Rhys Rowlands,
OL,8,Fsaid the "depraved" defendant had
OL,9,Fdeceived both boys. He noted the
OL,10,Fsecond boy was told to send more
OL,11,Fimages and threatened in capital
OL,12,Fletters that images would be shared
OL,13,Fonline if he didn't.
OL,15,FJailing Fuge, Judge Rowlands ordered
OL,16,Fhim to sign the sex offender register
OL,17,Fand be made subject to a sexual harm
OL,18,Fprevention order both for ten years.
